@node MWBTC.LHA "MWBTC.LHA"

Short:    MWB icons and dock-anims for TimeConnect
Uploader: egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Author:   egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Version:  1.0
Type:     pix/mwb


This package contains several icons and dock-anims for TimeConnect, all  in
the MWB style:

Short:    Phone Call coster/logger with MUI
Author:   jeffp@club-internet.fr (Jean-François PICK)
Version:  1.30
Type:     comm/misc


This package is Email-Ware. If you like the icons/dock-anims and  use  them
regularly,  you  are obligated to send me E-mail (if you have E-mail access
that is).

  E-mail: egerard@club-internet.fr

You can write in french or in english.


