@node MAGICCOUNTRY.LHA "MAGICCOUNTRY.LHA"

Short:    Set of icons "localized" for developers
Author:   egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Uploader: egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Type:     pix/mwb


This archive contains many MagicWB-style icons :

    * AmigaGuide
    * Doc
    * Drawer
    * Install
    * Readme

Each icons have an flag representative of an country :

    * Dansk
    * Deutsh
    * English
    * Espańol
    * Français
    * Italiano
    * Nederlands
    * Norsk
    * Polski
    * Portuguęs
    * Swenska


This package is Email-Ware. If you like the icons and use  them  regularly,
you are obligated to send me E-mail (if you have E-mail access that is).

    E-mail: egerard@club-internet.fr

You can write in french or in english.


@{"Image 1" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview Images/COUNTRY1.GIF"}  @{"Image 2" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview Images/COUNTRY2.GIF"}  @{"Image 3" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview Images/COUNTRY3.GIF"}

@{"Image 5" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview Images/COUNTRY5.GIF"}  @{"Image 4" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview Images/COUNTRY4.GIF"}

@endnode

@node MAGICDOCK.LHA "MAGICDOCK.LHA"

Short:    Set of dock-anims for MWB with an size of 32x30 pixels.
Author:   egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Uploader: egerard@club-internet.fr (Eric Gerard)
Type:     pix/mwb



This archive contains many MagicWB style dock-anims mainly  for  an  screen
like 640x512.


This package is E-MailWare. This means you can copy it freely  as  long  as
you  don't  ask any money for it, except perhaps a nominal fee for copying.
If you like and use this package, you MUST send to me an E-Mail.

    E-mail : egerard@club-internet.fr


You can write in french or in english.


@{"Image 1" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview Images/MWBDOCK1.GIF"}

@{"Image 2" SYSTEM "SYS:Utilities/Multiview Images/MWBDOCK2.GIF"}

@endnode

